These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: june, january, october, november, february
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: crime, family, satire, western, zombie
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: lily, begonia, iris, daffodil, sunflower
5 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, lizard, rabbit, rat
 1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 3. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 5. the owner of the bird is the person watching crime movies##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 7. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
10. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
11. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who growsbegonia and the person watching zombie movies##2
12. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
13. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Birthday      | june        | january | february     | october   | november |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | family      | western | zombie   | crime    |
| Flower   | daffodil  | begonia     | lily | iris | sunflower  |
| Pet           | chinchilla | lizard      | rat     | rabbit   | bird     |

