.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: gardening, hiking, reading, skydiving, writing
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: drama, crime, animation, comedy, romance
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, indian, polish, spanish
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: august, january, september, february, june
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is in the middle##1
 2. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the dutch##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is between the chinese and the person watching romance movies##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 7. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 8. the indian is the person watching comedy movies##1
 9. the indian is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
10. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
11. the indian is the person who's hobby is reading##1
12. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | gardening | writing    | hiking  | reading    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance    | crime       | animation      | drama | comedy        |
| Nationality   | spanish   | dutch     | chinese    | polish  | indian     |
| Birthday     | september    | january | june | february | august |

