.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, documentary, family, martial-arts, superhero
City: berlin, rome, san-francisco, paris, nizza
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, december, march, september, july
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is the person traveling to rome##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in september is in the middle##1
 3. the person traveling to paris is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 7. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 9. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
10. the person who's birthday is in january is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
13. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person watching superhero movies and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | collecting | singing     | puzzles   | filmmaking   | rock-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | documentary | adventure | martial-arts | family        |
| City   | san-francisco      | rome      | paris       | nizza       | berlin       |
| Birthday         | december | july  | september    | january    | march        |

