.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
There 5 different types of food: artichoke, onion, papaya, tomato, watermelon
There are 5 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, water
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, funk, indie, reggae, rock
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: rowing, skiing, baseball, surfing, ice-hockey
 1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 3. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the fan of reggae and the person eating tomato##2
 5. the person eating onion is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the fan of rock is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 7. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 8. the person drinking water is the fan of funk##1
 9. the fan of rock is in the middle##1
10. the fan of reggae is the person who's sport is rowing##1
11. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
12. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the fan of indie##1
13. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Food          | watermelon  | papaya     | tomato   | onion     | artichoke |
| Beverage         | water | hot-chocolate    | coffee  | lemonade | almond-milk   |
| Music-Genre   | funk        | dubstep    | rock     | indie     | reggae    |
| Sport   | skiing    | baseball | surfing | ice-hockey | rowing   |

