.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, old-henry, tiparillo, pall-mall, game
There 5 different types of food: apricot, broccoli, lettuce, orange, watermelon
The people have 5 different jobs:  dancer, lawyer, manager, social-worker, writer
5 different games are played: chess, go, canasta, bridge, snooker
 1. the person playing go is on the right of the dancer##1
 2. the person eating orange is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 3. the game-smoker is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 4. the tiparillo-smoker is between the person playing go and the person eating apricot##2
 5. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 6. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the person eating orange##1
 7. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the lawyer##1
 8. the writer is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 9. the old-henry-smoker is on the far right##1
10. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the dancer##1
11. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
12. the social-worker is on the left of the dancer##1
13. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Cigar   | pall-mall       | game       | aristoff   | tiparillo      | old-henry    |
| Food       | watermelon | orange        | apricot       | lettuce       | broccoli |
| Job        | writer     | lawyer        | social-worker | dancer        | manager  |
| Game      | bridge | canasta | chess      | snooker | go  |

