The people prefer 5 different music-genres: indie, ambient, jazz, soul, salsa
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, australian, french, polish, turkish
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, rowing, skiing, volleyball
 1. the fan of indie is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 3. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 4. the owner of the fish is on the right of the french##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 6. the owner of the lizard is between the fan of salsa and the person who's sport is baseball##2
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is the turkish##1
 8. the australian is on the far right##1
 9. the fan of jazz is on the right of the french##1
10. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
11. the fan of soul is between the fan of salsa and the person who's sport is baseball##2
12. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the polish##1
13. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
| Pet      | mouse  | lizard      | fish   | rabbit   | hamster   |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | soul   | jazz   | ambient | indie     |
