.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, siglo, bongani, game, swisher
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, drawing, reading, traveling, video-games
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, golf, handball, sailing
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: september, december, january, august, march
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's sport is cricket##2
 2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the siglo-smoker is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 4. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
 9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
10. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
11. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's hobby is reading##2
12. the game-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
13. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Cigar    | bongani       | game    | swisher | siglo  | fonseca        |
| Hobby       | video-games | card-games | reading  | traveling | drawing    |
| Sport       | golf        | handball   | cricket  | sailing   | basketball |
| Birthday   | august       | january      | march      | september | december  |

