.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: sunflower, aconite, tulip, daisy, azalea
The people have 5 different jobs:  bartender, engineer, entrepreneur, fisherman, pilot
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, crime, fantasy, scientific
5 different pets are kept: mouse, ferret, chinchilla, goldfish, bird
 1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 2. the fisherman is between the person watching crime movies and the entrepreneur##2
 3. the person who growsdaisy is the fisherman##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 6. the person who growsdaisy is between the pilot and the owner of the ferret##2
 7. the owner of the goldfish is the person who growstulip##1
 8. the person who growssunflower is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 9. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the pilot##1
10. the bartender is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
11. the entrepreneur is the person watching animation movies##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
13. the person who growsazalea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
