5 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, guinea-pig, lizard, mouse
The people have 5 different jobs:  dressmaker, entrepreneur, fisherman, chef, teacher
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
 2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the teacher##1
 4. the fisherman is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is between the person watching horror movies and the owner of the cat##2
 6. the person watching horror movies is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is between the dressmaker and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is entrepreneurd-games##2
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who's hobby is entrepreneurd-games##1
10. the person who's hobby is entrepreneurd-games is on the right of the person watching action movies##1

