.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cricket, swimming, volleyball, weightlifting, sailing
House: craftsman, wooden, townhouse, futuristic, cottage
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, blues, electronic, reggae, rock
There are 5 different nationalities: american, australian, egyptian, malaysian, thai
 1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the craftsman house##1
 2. the cottage house is between the malaysian and the fan of rock##2
 3. the fan of rock is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 4. the cottage house is the fan of ambient##1
 5. the fan of ambient is between the thai and the fan of electronic##2
 6. the thai is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 7. the townhouse house is the fan of reggae##1
 8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the fan of blues##1
 9. the american is the fan of blues##1
10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the egyptian##1
11. the cottage house is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
12. the wooden house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Sport         | volleyball    | sailing  | swimming  | cricket      | weightlifting |
| House   | wooden    | cottage   | futuristic | townhouse | craftsman   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | ambient    | rock    | reggae       | blues         |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | australian | thai    | egyptian     | american      |

 